@startuml
autonumber
actor "ATCC" as ATCC
participant "RouteController" as Ctrl
participant "SearchAlternativeRoutesUseCase" as UC
participant "RouteRepository" as Repo
database "Database" as DB

ATCC -> Ctrl : GET /api/routes/alternatives?origin=LIS&destination=MAD
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> UC : execute(originCode, destinationCode)
activate UC

UC -> Repo : findByOriginIataCodeAndDestinationIataCodeAndActiveTrue(origin, destination)
activate Repo
Repo -> DB : SELECT * FROM routes\nWHERE origin_iata = ? AND destination_iata = ?\nAND is_active = true
activate DB
DB --> Repo : direct routes
deactivate DB
Repo --> UC : List<Route> (directRoutes)
deactivate Repo

UC -> Repo : findByOriginIataCodeAndActiveTrue(originCode)
activate Repo
Repo -> DB : SELECT * FROM routes\nWHERE origin_iata = ? AND is_active = true
activate DB
DB --> Repo : first-leg routes
deactivate DB
Repo --> UC : List<Route> (fromOrigin)
deactivate Repo

UC -> Repo : findByDestinationIataCodeAndActiveTrue(destinationCode)
activate Repo
Repo -> DB : SELECT * FROM routes\nWHERE destination_iata = ? AND is_active = true
activate DB
DB --> Repo : second-leg routes
deactivate DB
Repo --> UC : List<Route> (toDestination)
deactivate Repo

note right of UC: Groups toDestination routes by origin IATA.\nFor each first-leg route whose destination\nmatches a second-leg origin,\ncreates an AlternativeRouteChain(firstLeg, secondLeg, stopover).

UC --> Ctrl : AlternativeRoutesResponse(origin, destination, directRoutes, oneStopRoutes)
deactivate UC

Ctrl --> ATCC : 200 OK (JSON Response)
deactivate Ctrl
@enduml
